<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=James_Stockdale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<p><a name="Online_references" id="Online_references"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=James_Stockdale&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Online references">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Online references</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.pbs.org/newshour/debatingourdestiny/interviews/stockdale.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pbs.org/newshour/debatingourdestiny/interviews/stockdale.html" rel="nofollow">Interview with Jim Lehrer on 1992 Vice-Presidential debate</a></li>
